verbose_text: Moreover, similarly to mOasl2, the expression of hOASL-3D inhibited the PR8 virus replication in both A549 and HeLa cells, induced rRNA degradation when inoculated with either pIC (500 ng/mL) or the PR8 virus (MOI = 1), and increased the expression of RNase L, IRF3, IFNalpha, IFNbeta, IFIT1, IL8, and TNFalpha in A549 cells.
